      <spirit:logicalName>HRESP</spirit:logicalName>
      <spirit:description>The transfer response, after passing through the multiplexor, provides the master with additional information on the status of a transfer.
When LOW, the HRESP signal indicates that the transfer status is OKAY.
When HIGH, the HRESP signal indicates that the transfer status is ERROR.</spirit:description>
